    • Method Detail

      • betweenLowerBoundInclusive

        public static <T extends Comparable<T>> org.hamcrest.Matcher<T> betweenLowerBoundInclusive(T from,
                                                                                           T to)
        Creates a matcher for Ts that matches when the compareTo() method returns a value between from and to, both included.

        For example: 

        assertThat(10, betweenLowerBoundInclusive(10, 11))
        will return true. while: 
        assertThat(11, betweenLowerBoundInclusive(10, 11))
        will return false.
